about.summary: Temporal SNA tools for continuous- and discrete-time longitudinal networks having vertex, edge, and attribute dynamics stored in the 'networkDynamic' format. This work was supported by grant R01HD68395 from the National Institute of Health.

name: r-tsna
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.3.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tsna
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/tsna_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/tsna/tsna_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: bba4b5e04ba647784581a2137f653f60b4c83cfd726c399556054c5a6d2cbd95

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-network >=1.13
    - r-networkdynamic >=0.9
    - r-statnet.common
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-network >=1.13
    - r-networkdynamic >=0.9
    - r-statnet.common

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('tsna')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('tsna')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://statnet.org
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Temporal SNA tools for continuous- and discrete-time longitudinal networks having
    vertex, edge, and attribute dynamics stored in the 'networkDynamic' format. This
    work was supported by grant R01HD68395 from the National Institute of Health.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
